it.unipr.sowide.actodes.interaction.Request

  • Packages that use Request 
    Package Description
    it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.buffer
    Shows how actors can implement the classical bounded buffer example through an implementation based on behavior change and one based on state change.
    it.unipr.sowide.actodes.interaction
    Provides classes and interfaces defining some message contents used in the basic interactions between actors.
    it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content
    Provides classes defining the message contents used for interacting with the group service.
    it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.mobile.content
    Provides classes defining the message contents used for interacting with the mobile service.
    it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.naming.content
    Provides classes defining the message contents used for interacting with the naming service.

    • Uses of Request in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.buffer

      Classes in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.examples.buffer that implement Request 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Get
      The Get enumeration defines a request that a Consumer actor sends to the actor managing the buffer for retrieving an its element.
      class  Put
      The Put class defines a request that a Producer actor sends to the actor managing the buffer for adding a new element to it.

    • Uses of Request in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.interaction

      Classes in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.interaction that implement Request 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Become
      The Become class defines a request asking an actor to move to another behavior.
      class  Create
      The Create class defines a request asking an actor or an actor space service provider to create a new actor.
      class  Forward
      The Forward class defines a request asking anactor to forward a message to another actor.
      class  Kill
      The Kill enumeration defines a request asking an actor to kill itself.
      class  Save
      The Save enumeration defines a request asking an actor to make a persistent copy of its state.
      class  Start
      The Start enumeration defines a request asking an actor to start itself.
      class  Stop
      The Stop enumeration defines an action used for asking an actor for stopping itself.

    • Uses of Request in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content

      Subinterfaces of Request in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  Group
      The Group interface identifies the possible message contents used for interacting with the group service.
      Classes in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.group.content that implement Request 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Cancel
      The Cancel class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to cancel a member from a group.
      class  Deregister
      The Deregister class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to remove a specific group.
      class  Link
      The Link class defines a task request, sent from an actor space service provider, for asking a remote actor space service provider to add the reference associated with the local group to the references of the remote group.
      class  Register
      The Register class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to register a specific group.
      class  Signup
      The Signup class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to add one or more actors to a group.
      class  Unlink
      The Unlink class defines a task request, sent from an actor space service provider, for asking a remote actor space service provider to remove the local group reference from the destinations of the remote group, because there are not more subscribers to the local group.

      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  Mobility
      The Mobility interface identifies the possible message contents used for interacting with the mobile service.
      Classes in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.mobile.content that implement Request 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Accepted
      The Accepted class defines a task request sent by an actor space service in response to a Transfer request if it accepted the mobile actor.
      class  Active
      The ActiveBehavior class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider for starting the mobile actor just arrived in its actor space.
      class  Move
      The Move class defines a task request asking the local actor space service provider for moving the actor to another actor space.
      class  Transfer
      The Transfer class defines a task request sent by an actor space service to another service provider for transferring a mobile actor.

      Classes in it.unipr.sowide.actodes.service.naming.content that implement Request 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Bind
      The Bind class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to bind the sender reference to the specified name.

      The Lookup class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to provide the reference of the actor bound to the specified name.

      The Subscribe class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to deliver the reference of the actor bound to a specified name.

      The Unbind class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to unbind the sender reference to the specified name.
      class  Unsubscribe
      The Unsubscribe class defines a task request asking an actor space service provider to cancel the subscription to the binding of an actor reference to a specified name.
